						</svg>
						Watch on YouTube
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="about" class="about">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">What is IBRAH?</h2>
				<div class="about-content">
					<p>
						<span class="highlight">IBRAH</span> is an Arabic word meaning "lesson," "reflection," or "warning taken from a story."
					</p>
					<p>
						Stories have always been humanity's oldest teacher. They carry wisdom, evoke emotion,
						and leave us changed. IBRAH is a platform dedicated to sharing short, impactful stories
						that resonate with your heart and awaken your mind.
					</p>
					<p>
						From real-life experiences to Islamic wisdom and social realities, every story we share
