						<p>Authentic experiences from everyday people that inspire, warn, and uplift.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<div class="card-icon">üïå</div>
						<h3>Islamic Stories</h3>
						<p>Timeless wisdom from Islamic history and teachings that guide the soul.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<div class="card-icon">üåç</div>
						<h3>Social Reality Stories</h3>
						<p>Bold narratives that reflect society's truths and challenge perspectives.</p>
					</div>
